# DarkBot.Net — Clean Architecture

Desktop-бот для DarkOrbit: **WPF** + Frida bridge + Unity client.

## Слои

| Проект | Роль | Зависит от |
|--------|------|------------|
| `DarkBot.Net.Core` | `I*Api`, domain models, `Options/` | — |
| `DarkBot.Net.Application` | bot loop, `I*AppService`, read models, mapping | Core |
| `DarkBot.Net.Infrastructure` | Frida, Unity, Login, Serilog, hosted sidecars | Core, Application |
| `DarkBot.Net.Presentation` | WPF, composition root | Application, Infrastructure |

```text
Presentation → Application (I*AppService), Infrastructure (только DI в Extensions/)
Infrastructure → Application, Core
Application → Core
```

## Core

- `Options/` — `DarkBotUiOptions`, `TestLoginOptions` и др.
- ❌ Нет WPF, Serilog host, Frida

## Application

- `Contracts/I*AppService` — **единственный** API для ViewModels
- `Models/Bot/` — read models для UI (`BotStatusSnapshot`, `MapStatusSnapshot`)
- `Services/` — реализации AppService; сборка snapshot/mapping **здесь**
- `Managers/`, `Bot/` — tick logic
- ❌ Нет WPF, XAML, UiStrings

## Infrastructure

- `Game/` — FridaGameApi, launcher, lifecycle
- `Hosting/` — `VerifierSidecarHostedService`
- `Logging/` — `DarkBotSerilogHostBuilderExtensions` (`UseDarkBotSerilog`)
- ❌ Нет ViewModels, XAML

## Presentation

- ViewModels → **только** `I*AppService` + `Ui/*` (окна, навигация)
- Snapshot: `_botStatus.Capture()` → `BotStatusSnapshot` **без** промежуточного mapper
- `Formatting/` — enum → `UiStrings`
- `Controls/Main/MapCanvas/` — render-only (`MapRenderSettings`, Skia drawers)
- `Extensions/DependencyInjection.cs` — composition root
- `Diagnostics/` — ReactiveUI/Splat probe
- ❌ `Services/`, `Models/`, `Mapping/`, `Configuration/`, `Logging/`
- ❌ ViewModel → Infrastructure-типы / Manager / `IMovementApi`
- ❌ Дублировать `Application.Models.Bot.*` в Presentation

## Пример VM

```csharp
// ✅
Snapshot = _botStatus.Capture();

// ❌
Snapshot = BotUiSnapshotMapper.ToUiSnapshot(_botStatus.Capture());
```

